  "title": "🌸 BEAUTICIAN (Beauty & Wellness | Additional Commission) 🌸",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Join our Expanding beauty & wellness team and turn your passion for skincare into a rewarding career!</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Provide personalized skincare advice and recommend suitable products based on individual customer needs</li><li>Perform facial treatments following customized facial plans to achieve desired skincare outcomes</li><li>Maintain cleanliness, hygiene, and sterilization of all treatment equipment to ensure a safe environment</li><li>Monitor and manage facial room supplies and inventory to support uninterrupted service delivery</li><li>Collaborate with team members to keep the treatment area clean, comfortable, and inviting for customers</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum 1 year of experience in the aesthetics or beauty industry</li><li>Passionate, self-motivated, and customer-oriented attitude</li><li>Strong interest in skincare and beauty treatments</li><li>Well-groomed with a positive and professional demeanour</li></ul><p><strong>What we Offer</strong></p><ul><li>5day per week</li><li>shift work time :9.45 a.m. to 6.45 p.m / 11:30 a.m. to 8:30 p.m.</li><li>Basic from $2300 - $3500</li><li>Additional Commission + Hands on fee</li></ul><p><strong>Other Information</strong></p><p>Staff Benefits 🎉 Birthday Leave with Celebration 🏥 Medical Coverage 💍 Marriage Leave & Gift 💰 Attractive High Commission Scheme 🧧 Company Lunch & Festive Gift Monthly Salary Range (SGD) $2,300 – $3,500 (Based on experience and performance)</p><p><strong>Location</strong></p><ul><li>PRIVILEGE BOUTIQUE ELITE - NAC</li><li>PRIVILEGE BOUTIQUE ELITE -PERENNIAL BUSINESS CITY</li><li>SPA - PRIVILEGE BOUTIQUE WELLNESS - WISMA</li></ul>",
